an></p></td></tr><tr style="height:24px"><td width="174" valign="center" rowspan="5" style="border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); padding: 5px;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:150%"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px">澳大利亚</span></strong></p></td><td width="345" valign="center" style="border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); padding: 5px;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:150%"><span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">迪肯大学</span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:24px"><td width="345" valign="center" style="border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); padding: 5px;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:150%"><span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">阿德莱德</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">大学</span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:24px"><td width="345" valign="center" style="border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); padding: 5px;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:150%"><span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">悉尼</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">科技大学</span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:24px"><td width="345" valign="center" style="border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); padding: 5px;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:150%"><span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">纽卡</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">斯尔大学</span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:24px"><td width="345" valign="center" style="border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); padding: 5px;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">西</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">悉尼大学</span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:24px"><td width="174" valign="center" style="border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); padding: 5px;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:150%"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px">新西兰</span></strong></p></td><td width="345" valign="center" style="border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); padding: 5px;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:150%"><span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">梅西大学</span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:24px"><td width="174" valign="center" style="border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); padding: 5px;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:150%"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px">韩国</span></strong></p></td><td width="345" valign="center" style="border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); padding: 5px;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:150%"><span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">东西大学</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">我校</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">合作院校均可在中国教育部留学服务中心进行学历认证的高校</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"> </span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"> </span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">萨塞克斯定向班</span> I</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;font-size: 21px">nternational Business<span style="font-family:宋体">（</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px">S</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;font-size: 21px">ussex<span style="font-family:宋体">）</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">英国萨塞克斯大学（</span>US<span style="font-family:宋体">）是世界前</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">1%</span><span style="font-family:宋体">的精英大学。</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">2018</span><span style="font-family:宋体">年我校成为全国唯一与萨塞克斯大学签订合作协议的独立学院，是国内首家与萨塞克斯大学进行本科联合培养的高校。目前，在国际商务、商务管理、金融学等三个专业开展“</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">2+2+1</span><span style="font-family:宋体">”项目合作。我校所有商科专业（涵盖管理学、经济学所有专业）均可对接萨塞克斯大学以上三个专业。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">2019<span style="font-family:宋体">年</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">3</span><span style="font-family:宋体">月萨塞克斯大学国际办公室的李希女士，在嘉华经面试为</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">17</span><span style="font-family:宋体">名来自金融工程、审计学、会计学的学生颁发“</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">2+2+1</span><span style="font-family:宋体">”</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">OFFER</span><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">2019<span style="font-family:宋体">年开设国际商务</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">2+2+1</span><span style="font-family:宋体">萨塞克斯大学定向班。定向班专业课采用中英双语及全英教学，与英国萨塞克斯大学共同开发</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体">门国际课程，全部由英国萨塞克斯外籍教师全英文授课。本科在萨塞克斯大学就读期间可获得带薪实习的机会，并有资格参加萨塞克斯</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">Start up</span><span style="font-family:宋体">项目，参与由萨塞克斯创意中心顾问主讲的工作坊，获得创业相关指导，并有机会赢取</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">Start up</span><span style="font-family:宋体">奖金。学生可获得我校和萨塞克斯大学本科双学位，再继续攻读一年研究生课程，可获得萨塞克斯大学硕士学位。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"> </span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">精英计划</span> </span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;font-size: 21px">Elite Program</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">为满足学生出国留学后继续攻读硕士研究生的个性化需求，学校</span>2019 <span style="font-family:宋体">年特别推出本硕直通“精英计划”项目，为每位学生配备</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体">对</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体">的导师，指导学生完成学业，帮助提升语言成绩、专业课绩点、留学背景等。保证学生</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">100%</span><span style="font-family:宋体">实现海外升硕的学历提升目标，助力学生申请到全球排名更好的世界名校。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://static-data.eol.cn//upload/image/201906/core_1559960920_7043_thumb.png" title="core_1559960920_7043_thumb.png"/></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">独一无二大学</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">体验</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">Unique experience</span></strong></p><p><img src="https://static-data.eol.cn//upload/image/201906/core_1559960920_1279_thumb.png" title="core_1559960920_1279_thumb.png"/></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">国际名师</span> </span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;font-size: 21px">International Renowned Scholars</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">为进一步融合中西方办学理念，整合国际优质教育教学资源，学校聘请了包括诺贝尔经济学奖获得者</span>---<span style="font-family:宋体">埃里克·马斯金（</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">EricMaskin</span><span style="font-family:宋体">）教授等一大批国际知名学者、政、商界人士为我校国际导师。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">Allan Cohoon<span style="font-family:宋体">加拿大皇家大学校长</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">Rhodri Morgan<span style="font-family:宋体">英国斯旺西大学校长</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:Batang;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Batang">장제국</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"> </span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">韩国东西大学校长</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">Philip Laird<span style="font-family:宋体">加拿大西三一大学副校长</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">Dean Fortin<span style="font-family:宋体">加拿大维多利亚市前市长</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">Ba</span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">r</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">ry</span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"> </span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">Cooper<span style="font-family:宋体">澳大利亚迪肯大学商学院院长</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">ACCA</span><span style="font-family:宋体">协会全球主席</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">Katherine Boxall<span style="font-family:宋体">英国创意艺术大学创意商学院副院长</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">Lyndsay Duthie<span style="font-family:宋体">英国创意艺术大学电影传媒学院院长</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">Gioia Pescetto<span style="font-family:宋体">英国朴茨茅斯大学商学院院长</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">JingJingXu<span style="font-family:宋体">英国普利茅斯大学商学院院长</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">（部分）</span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">雅思教学</span> IELTS training</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">针对参加</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">本硕直通项目的学生，学校设置雅思英语作为专业必修课，每周</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">12</span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">-16</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">节</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">；学校有专门的雅思教学团队；雅思教学实行小班授课，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">以</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">“</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">课堂讲解</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">-<span style="font-family:宋体">活动</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">教学</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">-<span style="font-family:宋体">高效练习</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">-</span><span style="font-family:宋体">及时反馈</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">-</span><span style="font-family:宋体">有效答疑</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">”</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">为主线</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。通过</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">教学</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">培养学生</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">听说读写能力，确保取得理想的雅思考试成绩，达到出国学习的语言要求，为将来</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">在国外</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">完成学业奠定基础。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"> </span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">国际课程</span> International classes</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">学校与国际合作院校共同开发了近</span> 20 <span style="font-family:宋体">门国际课程，全部由合作院校外籍教师来校讲授，使学生在出国之前熟悉国外授课方式、掌握专业词汇，为出国深造平稳过渡奠定基础</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-align:center;line-height:150%"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">合作课程一览表（部分）</span></span></strong></p><table border="0" cellspacing="0" width="565"><tbody><tr style="height:45px" class="firstRow"><td width="49" valign="center" style="border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); padding: 5px;"><p style=";text-align:center;vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-family: 华文宋体;font-size: 16px">序号</span></p></td><td width="184" valign="center" style="border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); padding: 5px;"><p style=";text-align:center;vertical-align:middle"><strong><span style="font-family: 华文宋体;font-size: 16px">课程名称</span></strong></p></td><td width="164" valign="center" style="border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); padding: 5px;"><p style=";text-align:center;vertical-align:middle"><strong><span style="font-family: 华文宋体;font-size: 16px">合作院校</span></strong></p></td><td width="169" valign="center" style="border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); padding: 5px;"><p style=";text-align:center;vertical-align:middle"><strong><span style="font-family: 华文宋体;font-size: 16px">授课教师</span></strong></p></td></tr><tr style="height:87px"><td width="49" valign="center" style="border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); padding: 5px;"><p style=";text-align:center;vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size: 16px">1</span></p></td><td width="184" valign="center" style="border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); padding: 5px;"><p style=";text-align:center;vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size: 16px">Cost Accounting</span></p></td><td width="164" valign="center" style="border-width: 1p