-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">精鹰计划</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">” </span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">加拿大</span>——</span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">“</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">青年</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">领袖训练营</span>”</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">澳大利亚</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">——“</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">澳洲领航行动</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">” </span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">法国</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">——“</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">艺术沙龙</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">” </span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">奥地利</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">——“</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">文化</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">体验营</span>”</span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">成就</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">更好的自己</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"> </span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;font-size: 21px">TO BE THE BEST YOU CAN BE</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://static-data.eol.cn//upload/image/201906/core_1559961081_8522_thumb.png" title="core_1559961081_8522_thumb.png" alt="core_1559961081_8522.png"/></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">微留学</span> Micro study tour</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">“微留学”是学校实现国际化办学目标，拓宽学生国际视野、满足国际化人才培养需求而设置的必修课程。学校已在加拿大维多利亚市建立了北美分校，在英国、美国、澳大利亚、法国、奥地利建立了海外教学中心。该课程由学生自主选择微留学国家，为期近两周，费用由学校承担。</span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">就业保障</span> employment security</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">学校</span>2016 <span style="font-family:宋体">届、</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">2017</span><span style="font-family:宋体">届和</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">2018 </span><span style="font-family:宋体">届毕业生就业率分别为</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">98.59%</span><span style="font-family:宋体">、</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">99.35%</span><span style="font-family:宋体">、</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">96.14%</span><span style="font-family:宋体">，连续</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">5</span><span style="font-family:宋体">年居独立学院前列。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">毕业生就业去向：世界</span>500<span style="font-family:宋体">强企业（</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">Google</span><span style="font-family:宋体">公司、中石化、亚马逊、苹果等）、各类会计师事务所、银行（中国工商银行、中国农业银行、中国建设银行、招商银行、中国民生银行、中国光大银行等）以及各类国有企业、机关、事业单位、三资企业等。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://static-data.eol.cn//upload/image/201906/core_1559961118_4618_thumb.png" title="core_1559961118_4618_thumb.png" alt="core_1559961118_4618.png"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">数据</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">来源：</span>“2018</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">北京地区</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;font-size: 14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">高校毕业生就业质量年度报告</span>”</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"> </span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">学校积极融入行业，开展与行业（企业）高度融合的实践教学，与北京工商银行、杭州银行、华林证券、新思路数字视觉等</span>168<span style="font-family:宋体">家企事业单位建立了良好合作关系。通过课程开发、实践操作、订单式培养、承接对口业务等方式，使学生专业与未来职业对接。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://static-data.eol.cn//upload/image/201906/core_1559961141_9008_thumb.png" title="core_1559961141_9008_thumb.png" alt="core_1559961141_9008.png"/></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">据新浪报道</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">软</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">科系统收集整理了全国所有本科层次高校的</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">2017<span style="font-family:宋体">年</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">毕业生就业质量报告，其中公布深造率数据的有</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">73<span style="font-family:宋体">所</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">民办高校及</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">193<span style="font-family:宋体">所</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">独立学院。北京</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">工商</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">大学嘉华学院以毕业生深造率</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">23.82</span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">%<span style="font-family:宋体">远高于全国高校</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">16.4</span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">%<span style="font-family:宋体">的</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">平均</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">水平，位居民办院校与独立学院</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">榜首</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，一流学科建设高校本科毕业生的平均深造率为</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px">31.4</span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">%<span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://static-data.eol.cn//upload/image/201906/core_1559961172_6545_thumb.png" title="core_1559961172_6545_thumb.png" alt="core_1559961172_6545.png"/></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">学生</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:宋体">代表</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px"> H</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;font-size: 21px">onor Graduates </span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">李佳璐，深造</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">院校</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">：</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">南安普顿大学</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://static-data.eol.cn//upload/image/201906/core_1559961250_5847_thumb.png" title="core_1559961250_5847_thumb.png"/></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">潘</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">宇</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，就业单位</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">：</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">德勤</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">会计师事务所</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://static-data.eol.cn//upload/image/201906/core_1559961251_5783_thumb.png" title="core_1559961251_5783_thumb.png"/></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">王泽晨，考研院校</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">：北京大学</span></span></p><p><img src="https://static-data.eol.cn//upload/image/201906/core_1559961251_1510_thumb.png" title="core_1559961251_1510_thumb.png"/></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">杨</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">翕涵</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，深造院校</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">：英国伯明翰大学</span></span></p><p><img src="https://static-data.eol.cn//upload/image/201906/core_1559961251_6049_thumb.png" title="core_1559961251_6049_thumb.png"/></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">龙静怡，深造院校</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">：埃克</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">塞</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">特大学</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://static-data.eol.cn//upload/image/201906/core_1559961252_2953_thumb.png" title="core_1559961252_2953_thumb.png"/></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体"></span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">梁思圣</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，获</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">英国</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">萨塞克斯大学</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"> <span style="font-family:宋体">美国</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">堪萨斯州立大学和天普大学</span>offer</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://static-data.eol.cn//upload/image/201906/core_1559961252_2333_thumb.png" title="core_1559961252_2333_thumb.png"/></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">肖</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">宇</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">洁</span> <span style="font-family:宋体">就业单位</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">：上海国际设计中心</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://static-data.eol.cn//upload/image/201906/core_1559961252_1618_thumb.png" title="core_1559961252_1618_thumb.png"/></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">张兰婷</span> <span style="font-family:宋体">获</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">诺丁汉大学</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">约克大学、纽卡斯尔大学等无所大学硕士</span>offer</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">深造院校：约克大学</span></span></p><p><img src="https://static-data.eol.cn//upload/image/201906/core_1559961253_8675_thumb.png" title="core_1559961253_8675_thumb.png"/></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">吴</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">蔚参加联合国经社理事会青年论坛</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://static-data.eol.cn//upload/image/201906/core_1559961253_1959_thumb.png" title="core_1559961253_1959_thumb.png"/></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">胡京缘，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">就业单位：毕马威华振会计师事务所</span></span></p><p><img src="https://static-data.eol.cn//upload/image/201906/core_1559961254_8263_thumb.png" title="core_1559961254_8263_thumb.png"/></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">朱雨桐</span> <span style="font-family:宋体">深造院校</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:宋体">：悉尼大学</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://static-data.eol.cn//upload/image/201906/core_1559961254_8913_thumb.png" title="core_1559961254_8913_thumb.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br/></p>', 'status': '1', 'update_time': '2019-06-08 10:39:45', 'type_name': '学校概况'}